    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おおおおっ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woooah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この力、すばらしい……
これが本格稼動すれば、
戦局は我が方へ転がる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This power is fantastic... With this
on the field, we will surely have
the upper hand in the war!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274472</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この力があれば、
エリュシオンを統べることすら、
可能かもしれないな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With this weapon...taking control
of Elysium will be rather easy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスの、ですか。
それはまた大きく出ましたな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos is still on his way,
though. That's a big factor.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁ、いいではないですか、
ふぉふぉ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He might as well not be, now.
Hahahahaha!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よくやったな、メルティア。
おまえの頭脳は明日を開く力だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You have done well, Meltia. Thanks to
your intellect, we will be able to secure
a better future for everyone.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとうございます、
お父様</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you very much, father.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274984</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>礼を言うのはこちらの方だ。
おまえの父親でよかったよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The one who should be thanking
you is me. I am so very proud
to be your father.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275052</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, you're making me blush...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これで我々はエリュシオンを、
あのダオスにすら対抗できる力を
手にしたのだからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With this, you have granted us the
capability to stand against Elysium
and Dhaos on the battlefield.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275280</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>決戦は&lt;Red&gt;ウェーランド&lt;White&gt;だ。
既にディオス率いる部隊は
現地に待機している</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right now Dios is leading the army
into a decisive fight in &lt;Red&gt;Wayland&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>博士、マナの消費量について
気になることが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Doctor, would you please see this?
The amount of Mana consumed is off
the charts...this is rather unsettling...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何か失敗でも……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it really something we
should worry about...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ、そうでは
ないのですが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>N-No, I don't think so...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ構わないわ。
実験は成功よ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then there's no problem. The
experiment was a success.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>構わない……
お父様が喜んでくださるなら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's no problem....because
father finally acknowledged me...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_290_040_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お父様が私を愛して下されば、
私を、必要として下されば</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I need father's love to keep going and I
would do anything he says, just for him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
